==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*τιμή / timē / tee-may'

===Etymology===
*From [[τίνω]]; 

===Noun===
'''τιμή'''

# A [[value]], that is, [[money]] paid, or (concretely and collectively) valuables; by analogy [[esteem]] (especially of the highest degree), or the [[dignity]] itself: - [[honour]], precious, [[price]], some.

